---
By: Marcus Aurelius
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 163
    Verse: 11
Tags:
  - Fault-finding
---
Regarding that which happens in harmony with nature, we ought to blame neither
gods, for they do nothing wrong either voluntarily or involuntarily, nor men,
for they do nothing wrong except unconsciously. Consequently, we shall blame
no one.
